comparators of integral writable types are not transitive for inequalities
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

         Key: HADOOP-176
         URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-176
     Project: Hadoop
        Type: Bug

  Components: io  
 Environment: red hat
